bitwarden-cli (2026.3.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bump nodejs dependency to (>= 20). Upstream requires Node.js >= 22.12,
    and Node.js 18 triggers a WASM panic in `bw generate` due to the
    getrandom crate's ES-module limitation.
  * Aggressively prune bundled node_modules (remove *.md, *.d.ts, dotfiles,
    build metadata, tsconfig, platform-foreign sass-embedded builds).
    License/copyright files are preserved.
  * Expand lintian overrides to cover bundled node_modules/* wildcards.

